including PubMed, Embase, CINAHL, Web of Science, PsycINFO, ProQuest 
Dissertations and Theses, Cochrane Library, China National Knowledge 
Infrastructure, and Wanfang. Assessment of methodological quality, data 
extraction, data synthesis, and assessing certainty in the findings will be 
conducted using the COSMIN methodology.
