Humerus Metastases.

El Motassime A(1), Meschini C(1)(2), Di Costa D(1), Rovere G(1)(2), Matrangolo 
MR(1), De Maio F(3), Farsetti P(3), Ziranu A(1)(2), Maccauro G(1)(2), Vitiello 
R(1)(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Orthopaedics, Fondazione Policlinico Universitario Agostino 
Gemelli IRCCS, 00168 Rome, Italy.
(2)Department of Orthopaedics, Fondazione Policlinico Universitario Agostino 
Gemelli IRCCS, University Cattolica del Sacro Cuore, 00168 Rome, Italy.
(3)Department of Clinical Science and Translational Medicine, Section of 
Orthopaedics and Traumatology, University of Rome "Tor Vergata", 00133 Rome, 
