Systemic sclerosis associated interstitial lung disease: a survey of current 
practices in France.

Nicolas A(1)(2)(3), Leroy S(4)(5), Mouthon L(6), Uzunhan Y(7), Cottin V(8), 
Mekinian A(9), Queyrel V(10)(5), Hachulla E(2)(3)(11)(12), Gachet B(13), Launay 
