'Skeletal Age' for mapping the impact of fracture on mortality.

Tran T(1)(2)(3), Ho-Le T(1), Bliuc D(2)(3), Abrahamsen B(4)(5)(6), Hansen L(7), 
Vestergaard P(8)(9)(10), Center JR(2)(3)(11), Nguyen TV(1)(11)(12).

