Differences in gait parameters when crossing real versus projected everyday life 
obstacles in healthy children and adolescents.

Gröble S(1)(2)(3)(4), van Hedel HJA(5)(6), Keller JW(5)(6)(7), Ammann-Reiffer 
C(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Swiss Children's Rehab, University Children's Hospital Zurich, 
